        2/27/2014
    

DO NOT BANK WITH HSBC!  I had my mortgage, checking & brokerage accounts and credit card with HSBC at  one point.  They provided the WORST customer service.  The Palo Alto branch account manager never responded to my calls or emails.  The only way to talk to her was to keep calling back hoping one time she would pick up the phone.This bank has countless, doesn't-make-sense policies.  For example,  I called to get a copy of my 1098 Form.  The rude representative said she couldn't mail one to me without my account number.  But she just looked up my account information using my SSN!  A simplest transaction must be done in writing via fax (no emails or phone).  This bank is ridiculous!  Exercise no common sense.  Poorest customer service.  I will never give business to them again.




