July 21, 2017 12:24 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of HSBC Securities (USA) Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
HSBC Securities (USA) Inc. is an investment banking firm that provides financial advisory services. The firm’s services include mergers and acquisitions, capital raising, privatization, and strategic advice. It was formerly known as Carroll McEntee & McGinley and changed its name in 1983. The firm is based in New York, New York. HSBC Securities (USA) Inc. operates as a subsidiary of HSBC Markets (USA) Inc.


HSBC Tower452 Fifth AvenueNew York, NY 10018United States



Phone: 212-525-3831

Fax: 212-525-0355








